text: ao kaunchaw a da. yeung ban banhchouh mk aoy puok anak nouv saamliek bampeak del ach betbang reangkay robsa puok anak ning saamliekbampeak samreab tengloma khluon . te saamliekbampeak kaotakhlach( thveuavei del a l laoh brae ning chiesaveang pi kar hamkhat)noh vea brasaer cheang avei teangoasa . teangnoh ku knongchamnaom phosdo tang robsa a l laoh sangkhumtha puokke nung changcham
